## vetiver_create_prototype { #vetiver_create_prototype }

`vetiver_create_prototype(data)`

Create zero row structure to save data types

### Parameters

| Name   | Type   | Description                                                         | Default   |
|--------|--------|---------------------------------------------------------------------|-----------|
| `data` | object | An object with information (data) whose layout is to be determined. | required  |

### Returns

| Type              | Description    |
|-------------------|----------------|
| vetiver.Prototype | Data prototype |
